  ('medical-tech-moex-00537', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '在健康成人骨髓中，下列各細胞數量的關係，何者正確？', '["Myeloblast＞Promyelocyte＞Myelocyte", "Myeloblast＜Myelocyte＜Promyelocyte", "Myeloblast＜Promyelocyte＜Metamyelocyte", "Myeloblast＝Metamyelocyte＝Myelocyte"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00538', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '小俊半年來體力變差，臉色蒼白，體育課沒跑幾下就氣喘如牛，且常抱著肚子走路，醫師檢查原來是脾臟腫 大。抽血發現白血球數為50×109/L，血小板數也高達800×109/L，白血球分類可見不成熟細胞，但以成熟細胞 居多，且嗜鹼性白血球高達10％。小俊並沒有發燒或其它感染的症狀。下列那些檢查最可以確定診斷小俊的 疾病？', '["核磁共振檢查", "超音波定位合併脾臟切片", "骨髓檢查合併染色體分析", "電腦斷層掃瞄／正子掃瞄"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00539', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那種組合最能區分急性淋巴球性白血病（acute lymphoblastic leukemia, ALL）與急性骨髓性白血病（acute myeloid leukemia, AML）？', '["ALL：SBB(+)；AML：MPO(+)", "ALL：NSE(+)；AML：ACE(+)", "+ + ALL：CD14 ；AML：CD45", "+ + ALL：TdT ；AML：CD117"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00540', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下圖所示之白血球形態，最可能出現於下列何種疾病？ A. Chédiak-Higashi syndrome', '["", "Neutrophil leucocytosis", "May-Hegglin anomaly", "Pelger-Huët anomaly"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00541', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '承上題，該疾病的嗜中性球之何種功能最不受影響?', '["Adhesion", "Phagocytosis", "Bacterial killing", "Chemotaxis"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00542', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '病人的凝血檢驗結果為PT正常，APTT延長，病人最有可能是那個凝血因子缺乏？', '["Factor VII", "Factor IX", "Factor X", "Tissue factor"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00543', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是臨床上platelet aggregation test常用的激活劑（agonist）？', '["Collagen", "ADP", "Heparin", "Epinephrine"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00544', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關factor XII的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["屬於接觸因子（contact factor），也是VKD（vitamin-K-dependent）凝血因子", "主要是經由HMWK水解而活化，負責啟動凝血內在途徑（intrinsic pathway）", "在體內與kallikrein及肝素（heparin）形成穩定複合體，可被帶負電的細胞膜磷脂質表面活化", "可被纖溶酶（plasmin）活化，參與維持體內凝血作用與纖溶作用的平衡"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00545', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關D-Dimer的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["是水解fibrinogen及fibrin皆可產生的纖溶蛋白分解物（fibrin degradation product, FDP）", "是thrombin與thrombomodulin所形成的複合體催化纖溶作用的產物", "在完全缺乏factor XIII的病人血液檢體中，可能檢測不到D-Dimer", "在實驗室中可用尿素溶解試驗（urea solubility test）檢測血漿中D-Dimer的含量"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-00546', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關臨床上抗凝血劑的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["肝素（heparin）是目前臨床上，使用最久的一種口服抗凝血劑（oral anticoagulant）", "在使用warfarin治療的最初五天至一週內，常須先以其他的抗凝血劑輔助，主要是因為warfarin亦會抑制 factor V和factor VIII", "Dabigatran是一種直接型口服抗凝血劑（direct oral anticoagulants, DOACs），其作用機轉與warfarin不同", "臨床上常用的直接型口服抗凝血劑（DOACs，如Rivaroxaban）主要是抑制factor VII的活性，故須以 PT（prothrombin time）監控服藥者的凝血功能"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:30+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ad5ed40a5173", "answer_pdf_sha1": "53e64be1505b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
